        <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"><strong>Launch Date:</strong> November 28, 2025</li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"><strong>Launch Location:</strong> Satish Dhawan Space Centre, Sriharikota, India (ISRO)</li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"><strong>Satellite:</strong> 1P PocketQube, 50x58x64mm, 245g</li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"><strong>Orbit:</strong> 525km altitude, Sun-synchronous</li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"><strong>Participation:</strong> Free, open to everyone globally</li>
